00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:46.920
to make mocks of for this team?

00:23:46.920 --> 00:23:49.570
What is our prototype
going to be?

00:23:49.570 --> 00:23:52.480
So we voted and decided
as a team on that,

00:23:52.480 --> 00:23:55.520
