00:26:00.962 --> 00:26:03.170
that they were doing, and
they felt like they weren't

00:26:03.170 --> 00:26:05.150
collaborating that effectively.

00:26:05.150 --> 00:26:07.879
The UX designer said, why
don't we run a sprint?

00:26:07.879 --> 00:26:10.170
I think this would be a really
great opportunity for us

00:26:10.170 --> 00:26:12.450
