00:26:16.390 --> 00:26:20.760
really focused on collaboration
rather than user validation,

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:24.430
and pull the methods that
emphasize collaboration.

00:26:24.430 --> 00:26:30.070
So their goal was to explore
and build new interactions

00:26:30.070 --> 00:26:31.920
and experiences
for their product,

00:26:31.920 --> 00:26:34.670
but to do it together,
so with engineers

00:26:34.670 --> 00:26:36.920
as opposed to the designers
off creating ideas

00:26:36.920 --> 00:26:39.840
and then throwing
it over the fence.

00:26:39.840 --> 00:26:42.090
And their deliverables
were a set of features,

00:26:42.090 --> 00:26:43.830
prototypes, and a
game plan for how

00:26:43.830 --> 00:26:46.800
