together moving forward.

00:26:46.800 --> 00:26:49.790
They decided to give
their sprint its own name.

00:26:49.790 --> 00:26:50.800
They called it a blitz.

00:26:50.800 --> 00:26:54.080
And because it was wintertime
and their team nickname

00:26:54.080 --> 00:26:56.480
was Snowman, they
called it a blitzard.

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:58.990
And they wrapped up the
sprint by going to DQ

00:26:58.990 --> 00:27:02.820
