blizzard made for them.

00:27:02.820 --> 00:27:04.930
They really wanted to
create a safe sandbox

00:27:04.930 --> 00:27:08.170
where they could brainstorm
together effectively.

00:27:08.170 --> 00:27:13.250
So they all got together and
created shared knowledge,

00:27:13.250 --> 00:27:17.760
had lightning talks, brought in
information about their users,

00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:21.190
really took a look at what
were the pain points of them,

00:27:21.190 --> 00:27:23.250
what problems were they having.

00:27:23.250 --> 00:27:27.120
And they did this
sketching and prototyping,

00:27:27.120 --> 00:27:30.400
sketching and prototyping
sort of structure,

00:27:30.400 --> 00:27:32.820
sharing back with each other
after they started creating

00:27:32.820 --> 00:27:35.320
ideas throughout the process.

00:27:35.320 --> 00:27:40.320
So a much more cyclical cycle.

00:27:40.320 --> 00:27:42.060
Cyclical cycle.

00:27:42.060 --> 00:27:46.890
Their schedule looked like this,
where they spent the first day

00:27:46.890 --> 00:27:49.360
on a small portion
of understand,

00:27:49.360 --> 00:27:51.600
and then sketching and
prototyping and sharing back,

00:27:51.600 --> 00:27:52.850
and sketching and prototyping.

00:27:52.850 --> 00:27:55.820
And they found this to be a
really, really effective method

00:27:55.820 --> 00:27:58.090
for them.

00:27:58.090 --> 00:28:02.190
They have started
using this repeatedly

00:28:02.190 --> 00:28:03.190
